808
00:50:29,720 --> 00:50:32,360
<font color="#ffffff">NEXT EPISODE</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

809
00:50:32,440 --> 00:50:34,480
<font color="#ffffff">You won't die in vain, old man.</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

810
00:50:35,320 --> 00:50:36,360
