811
00:50:40,480 --> 00:50:41,800
<font color="#ffffff">What's wrong with my dad?</font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

812
00:50:57,960 --> 00:51:02,800
<font color="#ffffff"><i>I wish I knew if I ever crossed your mind</i></font><font color="#ffffff"></font>

813
00:51:03,920 --> 00:51:08,840
